this is a weapon dispenser prefab for css.
this spawns 3 weapons:
-ma4a1
-ak47
-xm1015(shotgun) 
they all hae full ammo
-m4a1(90+30clip)
-ak47(90+30clip)
-xm1015(28+7clip)
the pics are taken in a test map so you could see it ingame,map not included.
more prefabs like this with other weapons on their way.
i hope you have fun with this.
